description: BMO ESG Corporate Bond Index ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the Bloomberg Barclays MSCI Canadian Corporate Sustainability SRI Index, net of expenses. Securities held in the Index are a variety of investment grade corporate bonds issued domestically in Canada in Canadian dollars, which have a term to maturity greater than one year, and have a higher MSCI ESG rating than their peers.
name: BMO ESG Corporate Bond Index ETF
